<doc id="944335" wikidata="Q571037" url="?curid=944335" title="Muscazone">
<text>Muscazone is a toxic chemical compound. It is an amino acid found in European fly agaric mushrooms.

Consumption causes visual damage, mental confusion, and memory loss.

